What is hoos.in?

Hoos.in makes doing fun things with your friends easy. Share ideas for what you want to do and see who's interested, or check out your Social Forecast to quickly figure out what's going on with your friends. For more information, check out the 'How it Works' link at the top of the www.hoos.in homepage.

What's Up with Us?

